640
01:42:30,524 --> 01:42:33,086
We'll give you work, food,

641
01:42:33,606 --> 01:42:34,802
and even money.

642
01:42:35,248 --> 01:42:36,204
Two cents per day.

643
01:42:36,890 --> 01:42:38,483
If you don't surrender,

644
01:42:39,172 --> 01:42:40,811
once discovered,

645
01:42:40,893 --> 01:42:42,647
you'll be executed.

646
01:42:42,695 --> 01:42:43,367
Next row.

647
01:42:43,416 --> 01:42:45,409
Understood?

648
01:42:45,658 --> 01:42:46,694
Step forward.

649
01:42:51,663 --> 01:42:52,619
Next row.

