670
01:44:19,065 --> 01:44:19,896
Save me.

671
01:44:21,588 --> 01:44:23,068
Miss Jiang, save me.

672
01:44:33,919 --> 01:44:35,513
Take her back.

673
01:44:36,562 --> 01:44:38,076
Shut up.

674
01:44:40,645 --> 01:44:41,556
Stand back.

675
01:44:42,847 --> 01:44:44,919
Please talk to the commander.

676
01:44:49,614 --> 01:44:51,048
Just talk with him.

677
01:44:55,219 --> 01:44:58,055
Let the foreigners come forward.

678
01:45:05,629 --> 01:45:07,143
You are Chinese.

679
