Don't push.

680
01:45:16,359 --> 01:45:18,875
Miss Vautrin will work out a solution.

681
01:45:18,921 --> 01:45:20,196
Don't worry.

682
01:45:22,525 --> 01:45:23,800
They won't let them go.

683
01:45:27,569 --> 01:45:29,129
We would not be afraid of the enemies.

684
01:45:29,171 --> 01:45:29,683
I am not afraid.

685
01:45:29,731 --> 01:45:31,006
We are strong.

686
01:45:31,693 --> 01:45:32,843
