705
01:46:58,214 --> 01:46:59,534
Miss Jiang, save me.

706
01:47:02,178 --> 01:47:03,407
Miss Jiang, save me.

707
01:47:05,781 --> 01:47:06,498
Mr. Chen.

708
01:47:07,262 --> 01:47:08,059
Mr. Chen.

709
01:47:09,104 --> 01:47:09,821
My husband.

710
01:47:10,706 --> 01:47:11,456
This one?

711
01:47:13,709 --> 01:47:14,300
Get down.

712
01:47:16,992 --> 01:47:17,982
Miss Jiang.

713
01:47:20,675 --> 01:47:21,665
Miss Jiang, save me.

714
01:47:27,962 --> 01:47:30,114
