Don't push.

738
01:48:34,544 --> 01:48:35,455
Xiaodou.

739
01:48:40,630 --> 01:48:42,189
Kid, go away.

740
01:48:46,475 --> 01:48:47,750
Xiaodou.

741
01:49:05,573 --> 01:49:06,563
Sergeant.

